column6: 2.111=WebSocket support was added in Presto 2.7[260] but was disabled due to security reasons.[261] In Presto 2.11 protocol implementation was updated to version RFC 6455[262] which resolved security issue.
2.61=Geolocation support was added in Presto 2.5, but was not enabled by default until 2.6.[271][272][68][69]
